                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-629" type="given" value="CHARLES PETEE"></interp>CHARLES PETEE DAVIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I was sent for, and the prisoner was given into custody with the handkerchief—I have kept it ever since.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced and sworn to.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I went into the shop to buy a pinafore, I asked what he wanted; he said 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; I said I would give him 5<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; I set the child on the counter while I looked at the pinafore; there was a lot of</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184204040100"></xptr>
